{
  "id": "adv_main_02_09_02",
  "title": "東京編2章17話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_unrest-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "一回戦からトリエル対リズノワだって？\n勝ち上がるのがどっちになるか、初戦で決まるのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first round is TRINITYAiLE vs LizNoir?\nThen only one team will advance forward from the starting round…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.033333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "そんな偶然、本当にあり得る？\n出来過ぎな気もするけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is a coincidence like that even possible?\nIt seems way too convenient.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "抽選はあくまでも抽選。公平な結果よ\n後から出た目にとやかく言っても始まらないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A lottery is a lottery. It’s a fair result.\nNo use in crying over spilled milk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.466666666666665
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "戦うと決まったからには、正々堂々戦う\nそうでしょう、瑠依？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that’s it decided‚ we’ll fight fair and square.\nIsn’t that right‚ Rui?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.566666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はい。むしろ光栄です\n初戦で確実に莉央さん達と戦えるのは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. In fact‚ we’re honored…\nto battle against LizNoir in the first round.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "……トーナメントが進んでからだと\n戦えない可能性だってありましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ there was a chance\nwe wouldn’t run into you further along in the tournament.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "あら、言うじゃない。そのままお返しするわ\n……ステージ、楽しみにしてるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My‚ my. Confident‚ aren’t we? Right back at you.\nI look forward to seeing you on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.43333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7333.333333366667,
          "startTime": 47.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、葵？　どこかに行くのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio? Aoi? Where are you going?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "初戦の相手も決まったことだし\n寮に帰ってミーティングするのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now we know our opponent for the first match‚\nwe’re going back to the dorm for a meeting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 56.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ここでダラダラしていても無意味だもの\nそれじゃあ、また後でね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no point in lingering around here.\nWe’ll see you later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4700.000000000003,
          "startTime": 61.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、私達も失礼します",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’ll excuse us as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4133.333333399996,
          "startTime": 66.9666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10300.000000000004,
          "startTime": 73.1333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12675.333309200007,
          "startTime": 75.5086666425
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（本当なら俺も、何か声を掛けてあげたかった）\n（でも互いの事情も覚悟も察しているから、言えない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I want to say something to them‚ but I can’t.)\n(I guess at both of their feelings‚ their commitment.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（去っていく天動さん達の後ろ姿を）\n（眺めることしか出来ない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(All I can do is watch them)\n(as they walk away‚)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-koh004-01.m4a",
      "text": "（そんな自分が、無性に悔しかった……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(filled with frustration toward my own inadequacy.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n私達もこの後は、自由行動でもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}!\nCan we also have some time to ourselves after this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalseat-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalseat00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "これからについて\nグループ内でしっかり話し合っておきたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We want to sit down\nand have a discussion with our groups about our future plans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、もちろん\nそれじゃあひとまず、今日は解散しようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ of course.\nAlright‚ let’s call it quits for the day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4099.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 98.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_coast_night",
      "startTime": 98.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_liz-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 98.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "あー！　{user}さんお疲れ様です！\nいやー、とんでもない結果になっちゃいましたね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aah! Hey there‚ {user}!\nWell‚ that was a heck of a result!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだな。それにしては妙にテンション高いけど\n……愛、どうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah. You seem oddly hyper.\nIs everything okay‚ Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "初戦がトリエルって分かって\n凄いプレッシャーだったんだって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She felt a lot of pressure when she found out\nwe were up against TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もう平気ですよ！　初戦で強敵に勝っておけば\n後が楽ですからね！　あはははは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’m fine now! If we beat such a formidable opponent in the first round‚\nthe rest will be a walk in the park! Ahahaha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "おお～、さすが愛ちゃん！　切り替えが早いね～\n吹っ切れたようで何よりだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! Good stuff‚ Ai! You really switched up quick!\nGlad you got over your anxiety!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "むしろ吹っ切れ過ぎてヤケになっているような……\nそういうこころはどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She sounds like she’s surpassed anxiety and moved on to desperation…\nHow’re you doing‚ Kokoro?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんビックリしましたよ？\n愛ちゃんみたいに取り乱すほどじゃないですけど",
