      "text": "あの時、負けた僕らは解散って聞かされてたから\n今更何言い出すんだ……って思ったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Although‚ we’d been told that if we lost we’d be disbanded‚\nso‚ at the time… I had no idea why he was telling us that.",
