      "text": "ともかく……朝倉さんのあの言葉を聞いて、私自身も\nそんな予感をずっと抱いてたんだって気付いたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway… Mr. Asakura’s words made me realize\nwhat I’d been feeling myself for a long while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、同じ事務所に所属しているアイドルだし\nなかなか機会には恵まれなかったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But we both belonged to the same agency‚\nso we never had the opportunity…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
