      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_09_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "それでこの初戦は\nようやく叶った夢のカード……ってことなのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So what you’re saying…\nis that this first match… will be a dream come true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
