      "text": "あと、莉央としては白黒つけたいんでしょ？\n僕ら、よく比べられてたもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You also want to settle it once and for all‚ don’t you‚ Rio?\nWe used to get compared to TRINITYAiLE all the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
