      "text": "朝倉さんや姫野さん、果てはスタッフや世間からも\n比べられて、いい気なんてしないもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It didn’t feel good to be compared by Mr. Asakura‚\nMs. Himeno‚ and by the staff and the public as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 266.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
